1. On CMD
a. Run Qdrant:
(in cmd promt not powershell)
One-time setup:
bash:
docker volume create qdrant_data

docker run -d --name qdrant_server -p 7000:6333 -v qdrant_data:/qdrant/storage qdrant/qdrant

Daily start:
bash:
docker start qdrant_server

Daily stop:
bash:
docker stop qdrant_server

b. Run MongoDB:
mongod
c. Run Ollama mistral
ollama run mistral
2. Run main.py:
uvicorn main:app --reload
or
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8080
3. Check Database in MongoDB:
a. mongosh
b. show dbs
c. use
d. show collections
4. Check Qdrant DB and vectors
a. go to view_qdrant.py
b. python view_qdrant.py
